.el .ds Aq '
.TH ox-lock 1  "ox-lock " 
.SH NAME
ox\-lock \- Generate or verify a reproducibility lockfile
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBox\-lock\fR [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] <\fIsubcommands\fR>
.SH DESCRIPTION
Generate or verify a reproducibility lockfile
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
ox\-lock\-generate(1)
Generate an ox.lock file from the current workflow state
.TP
ox\-lock\-verify(1)
Verify the current state against an existing ox.lock
.TP
ox\-lock\-help(1)
Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)
